Faculty SenateChristi Hestand, Staff Senate For questions, please contact SPMC Secretary Shelly Beattie by email or at (940) 369-8400. Contact Us: Office of Space Management and Planning Voice: (940) 369-8400 http://osmp.unt.edu/ Email us: Have questions on content or technical issues? Please contact us. osmp@unt.edu UNT System: UNT Home UNT System UNT Dallas UNT Health Science Center Site last updated on March 2, 2017 Disclaimer | AA/EOE/ADA | Privacy Statement | Web Accessibility Policy | State of Texas Online | Emergency Preparedness 